00:01:36,820 --> 00:01:40,950
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 12]

4
00:01:45,030 --> 00:01:45,550
Ma Huai.

5
00:01:45,990 --> 00:01:46,720
In that case,

6
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:47,990
you're a nice person.

7
00:01:47,990 --> 00:01:49,720
But you strangled Lou Qingtai.

8
00:01:50,110 --> 00:01:51,570
This is a capital offense.

9
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,370
By the way, Ma Huai,

10
00:01:56,789 --> 00:01:57,870
I remember you said

11
00:01:58,110 --> 00:02:00,840
the first time you left the burial goods store...

12
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:14,300
That's exactly what the situation was.

13
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:20,400
When you went to stole from the burial goods store,

14
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,450
you also crossed the backyard, right?

15
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:23,530
Steal?

16
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:24,950
Backyard?

17
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:27,270
What are you talking about?

18
00:02:27,270 --> 00:02:29,000
The scribe recorded it clearly

19
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,870
that when you were interrogated last time, you said...

20
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:32,070
I was on duty last night.

21
00:02:32,070 --> 00:02:33,590
I left the government office at 9:30 p.m.

22
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:36,430
I arrived at the burial goods store at 9:45 p.m. at most.

23
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:38,140
I said a few words and left.

24
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:39,550
Right.

25
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:44,930
But I asked your friend

26
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:47,070
who was on duty with you that day.

27
00:02:47,829 --> 00:02:48,310
Yes.

28
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,160
It was Officer Niu that day.

29
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,640
No, Niu Daming.

30
00:02:51,670 --> 00:02:52,470
He was on duty.

31
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:02,570
Magistrate is so easy-going.

32
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:04,790
He invited a coroner to drink alcohol.

33
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,280
It's going to rain.

34
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,960
It should be fine today.

35
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:10,890
Keep an eye out.

36
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,010
I'm very sleepy.

37
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:13,590
I'm going to find a place to sleep.

38
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,080
Yes.

39
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:16,350
You didn't go to sleep.

40
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:18,110
Instead, you went to the burial goods store

41
00:03:18,110 --> 00:03:19,390
while Dugu Yang was away.

42
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:19,990
Nonsense!

43
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:21,850
What proof do you have?

44
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:25,190
Your shoes are quite new.

45
00:03:25,670 --> 00:03:27,329
The old ones are at your house.

46
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:29,730
You didn't have time to wash them, right?

47
00:03:36,579 --> 00:03:38,110
I found these at your house.

48
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:39,710
If you hadn't gone to the backyard of the burial goods store

49
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:40,770
on the rainy night,

50
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,710
how could the shoes be covered

51
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:43,480
with so much clay

52
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:46,010
exclusively used for making clay figurines?

53
00:03:46,670 --> 00:03:47,400
No, I didn't.

54
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:50,350
I had no reason to go to the burial goods store.

55
00:03:50,350 --> 00:03:52,350
For the Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal.

56
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,440
When I captured you, you said...

57
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,700
That seal has killed several people.

58
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:58,870
But no one has ever seen it.

59
00:03:59,230 --> 00:03:59,790
I think

60
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,140
it's a lie

61
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:01,950
that Dugu Yang

62
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:02,880
told to his wife.

63
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:05,250
There is no such thing in the world at all.

64
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,290
I didn't expect

65
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:07,750
that I would also be tricked

66
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,150
after working in the government office for many years.

67
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,790
You were tricked by Dugu Yang

68
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:13,440
when you were following Chuntiao, right?

69
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:15,410
[Lingdu]

70
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,980
Dong Haogu is nothing.

71
00:04:18,470 --> 00:04:20,680
His entire Treasure Pavilion

72
00:04:20,709 --> 00:04:21,839
isn't worth my seal.

73
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:26,800
The poor coroner has such a treasure?

74
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,720
Even though I went there, I didn't kill anyone.

75
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:34,290
Did I ever say you killed someone?

76
00:04:36,350 --> 00:04:37,909
When you were imprisoned,

77
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,260
you didn't see

78
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,390
Lou Qingtai's body.

79
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,180
I just deliberately said

80
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,640
that Lou Qingtai has died.

81
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,890
But you weren't surprised at all.

82
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,030
You're

83
00:04:49,659 --> 00:04:51,970
the person who killed Lou Qingtai.

84
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,290
Niu Daming.

85
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:30,910
Look.

86
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:32,320
What is this?

87
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:34,940
This is what I drew

88
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:36,390
based on what Qingniao said.

89
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:37,050
Niu Daming.

90
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,710
That day, Qingniao went to look for his brother

91
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:39,390
in the rain.

92
00:05:39,790 --> 00:05:41,630
But she found you coming out of the backyard.

93
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,700
She was so scared that she ran back home in a hurry.

94
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,480
That's why she missed the chance

95
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,610
to find his brother.

96
00:05:45,909 --> 00:05:46,350
She...

97
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,630
She's slandering me.

98
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:48,360
Torture him!

99
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:50,340
Magistrate Dugu, stop hesitating.

100
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,159
Without torture,

101
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,620
this thief won't confess.

102
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:53,870
Xu.

103
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:56,070
You also hit me when I'm down?

104
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:59,070
Assistant Xu is right.

105
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,550
I can give you some advice

106
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:04,720
on what kind of torture

107
00:06:04,990 --> 00:06:06,590
to use.

108
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:09,040
Tell the truth!

109
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:22,140
After I sneaked into the burial goods store,

110
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:23,310
I searched everywhere.

111
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,970
But I couldn't find that seal.

112
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,830
Suddenly, I heard some noise outside the window.

113
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:27,560
Who's there?

114
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:34,830
Officer Niu.

115
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,740
You're here to steal?

116
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:38,670
Lou Qingtai?

117
00:06:39,590 --> 00:06:41,190
I can keep the secret for you.

118
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:41,990
But you...

119
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,659
You have to give me justice.

120
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:46,030
Behead Ma Huai who poisoned my father

121
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,430
and Dugu Yang

122
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,310
who performed a fake autopsy.

123
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:50,230
I won't tell anyone

124
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:51,560
about you being a thief.

125
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,690
Okay.

126
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:11,300
Only the dead

127
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:13,370
won't tell anyone anything.

128
00:07:29,110 --> 00:07:29,730
Qingniao.

129
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:30,770
Qingniao.

130
00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:34,510
Qingniao.

131
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,350
Lu Lingfeng, impressive!

132
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,480
Now,

133
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:40,070
you're much better

134
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:41,890
than when you were in Nanzhou.

135
00:07:42,110 --> 00:07:42,700
Su Wuming.

136
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:44,420
You're good at teaching him

137
00:07:44,450 --> 00:07:45,850
on behalf of your master.

138
00:07:45,909 --> 00:07:46,750
In the court,

139
00:07:47,110 --> 00:07:49,440
don't say anything unrelated to the case.

140
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:51,140
This...

141
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,010
General Lu.

142
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:57,790
Please get it straight for me.

143
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:58,920
On that rainy night,

144
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,960
what happened

145
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:01,850
in the Lingdu Burial Goods Store?

146
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:05,430
Fine.

147
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,230
I'll begin now.

148
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:08,930
That night,

149
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:11,470
Dugu Yang went to the government office

150
00:08:11,470 --> 00:08:12,930
to drink with Magistrate.

151
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:17,130
Chunshan used the chance to sneak into the burial goods store.

152
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,790
Chunshan found some copper coins

153
00:08:22,790 --> 00:08:24,310
but was scared away

154
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,070
by the noise in the backyard.

155
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,080
It was Ma Huai who came to deliver clay.

156
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,450
Chunshan escaped.

157
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:33,919
In the backyard,

158
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,120
Ma Huai and Lou Qingtai

159
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:35,880
had a conflict.

160
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,320
You can't slander Coroner Dugu!

161
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:37,710
I...

162
00:08:39,429 --> 00:08:40,630
The rain poured down.

163
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,350
Ma Huai left.

164
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,230
Then,

165
00:08:44,070 --> 00:08:45,390
Niu Daming sneaked in

166
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:47,600
but met Lou Qingtai.

167
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:48,880
He killed Lou Qingtai.

168
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:50,830
But Ma Huai was worried

169
00:08:50,830 --> 00:08:52,960
that Lou Qingtai would harm Dugu Yang.

170
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:54,350
When he returned,

171
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,520
he found Lou Qingtai's body.

172
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,480
He thought he was the murderer.

173
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,400
In a panic,

174
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:01,790
he used the clay figurine to hide the body.

175
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,420
Next,

176
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:07,110
Dugu Yang returned to the burial goods store

177
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:09,380
and encountered the tomb robber, Lu Er.

178
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:12,030
[Lingdu Burial Goods Store]

179
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:21,410
Who is it?

180
00:09:22,070 --> 00:09:22,870
An old friend.

181
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,470
I don't know you.

182
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:31,350
But I know you.

183
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,630
We both deal with dead people.

184
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:36,310
Can't I be called as your old friend?

185
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,550
You're a tomb robber?

186
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:39,830
After that,

187
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,310
you

188
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,790
returned to the burial goods store again.

189
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,270
In order to save your life,

190
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:46,850
Dugu Yang killed Lu Er.

191
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:50,390
He did this, not me.

192
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:52,100
Then, you lost your gambling tool

193
00:09:52,100 --> 00:09:53,800
in the fight with Lu Er,

194
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:55,910
which exposed your whereabouts.

195
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,360
I know your family was rich before.

196
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,310
It's gambling that made you poor.

197
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:02,720
If it weren't for Dugu Yang's help,

198
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,550
you would have starved to death.

199
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:05,850
You're ungrateful

200
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:07,900
and even tried to blackmail him.

201
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:08,590
You're

202
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,950
such a rat.

203
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:11,910
You...

204
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:12,430
Mother.

205
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,630
Calm down.

206
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:15,460
Sit down.

207
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:17,310
Sit down and listen to him.

208
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:19,630
He's analyzing the case now.

209
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:22,020
What he said may not be true.

210
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:23,270
It may not be true.

211
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:25,390
Mother.

212
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:28,320
Lu Lingfeng.

213
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:29,430
Go on.

214
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:31,820
Then,

215
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,550
Dugu Yang gave a silver ingot to Chunshan

216
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:35,950
and asked him to leave Shiyang.

217
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:38,750
After that, he hid the body with the clay figurine.

218
00:10:39,590 --> 00:10:40,320
At this time,

219
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:43,130
you came to the burial goods store again,

220
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,640
probably regretting not handling

221
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,300
Lou Qingtai's body better.

222
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,310
You tried to test

223
00:10:49,610 --> 00:10:51,540
whether Dugu Yang had found it out.

224
00:10:55,950 --> 00:10:57,610
Why are you still here so late?

225
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,310
Aren't you afraid

226
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:02,170
that your wife will sleep with someone else?

227
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:26,930
Okay.

228
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,390
You're right again.

229
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:31,090
After Niu Daming left,

230
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,650
you, Boss Dong,

231
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,910
came to talk business.

232
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:40,030
I left home at 9:45 p.m.

233
00:11:40,430 --> 00:11:43,110
It took at most seven minutes and 30 seconds to get to the burial goods store.

234
00:11:43,110 --> 00:11:44,030
Dugu Yang promised

235
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:46,260
to sell the Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal to me.

236
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:47,630
I went home happily

237
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:48,600
to get the money.

238
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,140
When I came back,

239
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,370
he already died.

240
00:11:52,230 --> 00:11:54,780
I, Dong Haogu, am telling the truth.

241
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,340
Niu Daming.

242
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,310
The third time you sneaked into the burial goods store,

243
00:12:00,310 --> 00:12:01,510
you killed Dugu Yang.

244
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,030
Was it for Chuntiao

245
00:12:03,470 --> 00:12:04,480
or that seal?

246
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:05,190
I...

247
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:06,910
No, I didn't.

248
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:09,920
Here you are.

249
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:11,870
We also have the night watchman, Uncle Zhong, as the witness.

250
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,270
You still want to deny it?

251
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,600
Uncle Zhong was talking nonsense.

252
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:18,390
Indeed, I went back to the burial goods store again.

253
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:20,590
I also thought about killing Dugu Yang.

254
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:21,590
But...

255
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:38,570
But Dugu Yang wasn't there.

256
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,850
Lou Qingtai's body

257
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,090
also disappeared.

258
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,790
Nonsense.

259
00:12:43,190 --> 00:12:45,110
There were many paper people and paper horses there.

260
00:12:45,110 --> 00:12:46,350
Even if, as you said,

261
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:48,230
Dugu Yang wasn't in the store at that time,

262
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:50,230
how could he not put out the candles?

263
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:51,170
This...

264
00:12:51,350 --> 00:12:52,580
I don't know.

265
00:12:56,140 --> 00:12:57,540
You wanted to get the seal

266
00:12:57,710 --> 00:12:59,830
and lusted for Chuntiao because of her beauty.

267
00:12:59,830 --> 00:13:01,070
After killing Dugu Yang,

268
00:13:01,070 --> 00:13:03,430
you put the murder weapon in the hand of the clay figurine.

269
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:05,470
There was no sheriff in Shiyang County before.

270
00:13:05,470 --> 00:13:06,710
Once there were murder cases,

271
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,390
they would be given to you to deal with.

272
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:09,370
You wanted

273
00:13:09,590 --> 00:13:11,070
to cover up the case by saying

274
00:13:11,070 --> 00:13:13,200
that the clay figurine killed people.

275
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,320
Unfortunately,

276
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:16,270
the newly appointed Magistrate Dugu

277
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,770
investigated the case personally.

278
00:13:17,770 --> 00:13:18,950
His old friend also came a long way

279
00:13:18,950 --> 00:13:19,990
to help him.

280
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:22,630
You failed.

281
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:29,690
Killing one people

282
00:13:29,950 --> 00:13:30,750
costs my head.

283
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:33,510
Killing two people also costs my head.

284
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:35,390
Why would I deny it?

285
00:13:38,690 --> 00:13:40,490
Magistrate Dugu. Assistant Xu.

286
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,240
