00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:40,910
Su Wuming!

579
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:58,790
Are you Coroner Dugu?

580
00:29:06,630 --> 00:29:07,390
No.

581
00:29:08,630 --> 00:29:09,710
I remember

582
00:29:09,710 --> 00:29:10,910
you seemed to be dead.

583
00:29:11,100 --> 00:29:11,790
Dugu.

584
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,260
Do you

585
00:29:13,470 --> 00:29:14,790
have any regrets?

586
00:29:18,150 --> 00:29:19,070
Dugu Yang!

587
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:25,050
It's been ten days.

588
00:29:25,430 --> 00:29:27,030
Your wound is almost healed.

589
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,340
Why do you still have nightmares?

590
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,870
It's all because you played tough.

591
00:29:30,870 --> 00:29:32,680
You went to the trial as soon as you woke up.

592
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,470
The poison took effect again.

593
00:29:33,470 --> 00:29:34,400
You almost died.

594
00:29:34,870 --> 00:29:35,550
You even stole

595
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:37,280
the limelight from General Lu.

596
00:29:38,220 --> 00:29:39,270
No way!

597
00:29:40,870 --> 00:29:42,270
Why were you avoiding me?

598
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,990
Do you think that I, a woman from Jianghu,

599
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,110
am not worthy of you?

600
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:45,940
No.

601
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:47,150
I'd never been hurt

602
00:29:47,150 --> 00:29:48,070
so badly.

603
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:49,860
I already gave you half of my life.

604
00:29:49,860 --> 00:29:50,460
Su Wuming.

605
00:29:50,990 --> 00:29:52,310
As for the remaining half,

606
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:54,170
if you don't want it, just tell me.

607
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:55,200
No, I...

608
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:06,090
Did you chase me away because you knew

609
00:30:06,350 --> 00:30:08,150
you would encounter assassins?

610
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,950
You didn't want me to follow you

611
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,710
because you didn't want to get me in trouble.

612
00:30:12,710 --> 00:30:13,270
No...

613
00:30:14,150 --> 00:30:15,310
I guess

614
00:30:15,510 --> 00:30:16,840
that he should be awake.

615
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:20,590
Look. Look.

616
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:21,840
He woke up.

617
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:23,590
Fei. Xijun.

618
00:30:24,470 --> 00:30:26,000
Didn't I tell you before...

619
00:30:26,310 --> 00:30:26,910
She...

620
00:30:27,710 --> 00:30:29,440
You said you didn't want to see Yingtao.

621
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:30,670
But we couldn't stop her.

622
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:31,270
Right.

623
00:30:31,630 --> 00:30:33,310
You did something wrong to her.

624
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,480
Just apologize.

625
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,190
You're a man.

626
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,740
A man of integrity.

627
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:40,560
Is it so difficult

628
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,450
to say sorry?

629
00:30:41,670 --> 00:30:42,780
Do you think you could chase Yingtao away again

630
00:30:42,780 --> 00:30:44,230
if you refused to see her

631
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,070
this time?

632
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:46,110
It's like

633
00:30:46,150 --> 00:30:47,870
you don't explain to Lu Lingfeng.

634
00:30:47,870 --> 00:30:48,870
Doesn't he know

635
00:30:48,910 --> 00:30:50,710
you're doing it for his own good?

636
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:05,150
Yingtao.

637
00:31:06,940 --> 00:31:10,290
Please accept my bow.

638
00:31:16,820 --> 00:31:17,880
Don't just bow.

639
00:31:18,390 --> 00:31:20,150
Say what you should say.

640
00:31:25,070 --> 00:31:27,510
I'm not good at saying nice words.

641
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,290
You're not good at saying nice words?

642
00:31:31,290 --> 00:31:32,430
If you were not good at saying nice words,

643
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:33,670
we would all be mutes.

644
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,470
I seemed to dream

645
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:42,830
of Dugu Yang just now.

646
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:45,910
He asked me to go to the burial goods store

647
00:31:45,910 --> 00:31:46,630
again

648
00:31:47,710 --> 00:31:49,070
and find something for him.

649
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:49,670
Come back.

650
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,430
Is it money?

651
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:53,970
Lu Lingfeng has already found it.

652
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,570
You don't need to go.

653
00:32:36,970 --> 00:32:38,030
[Highly Skilled]

654
00:32:37,430 --> 00:32:38,310
We've reported the case

655
00:32:38,310 --> 00:32:39,910
to the Yongzhou Government.

656
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:41,270
These five silver ingots

657
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:43,270
were obtained by Dugu Yang from his teaching.

658
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,790
Now, they're returned to his family.

659
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:45,760
That's all?

660
00:32:47,230 --> 00:32:48,710
There were six silver ingots.

661
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:49,310
But Dugu Yang

662
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:50,210
gave one to Chunshan.

663
00:32:50,210 --> 00:32:51,150
There're five silver ingots left.

664
00:32:51,150 --> 00:32:51,710
They're all here.

665
00:32:51,710 --> 00:32:53,970
I'm not talking about the silver ingots.

666
00:32:54,870 --> 00:32:56,150
Didn't he leave me

667
00:32:56,190 --> 00:32:57,310
anything else,

668
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,950
even if it's just a few words?

669
00:33:14,670 --> 00:33:18,220
[A Letter of Divorce to Chuntiao by Dugu Yang]

670
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:23,470
A letter of divorce?

671
00:33:31,030 --> 00:33:31,910
General Lu said

672
00:33:32,190 --> 00:33:34,050
you can pretend it doesn't exist.

673
00:33:38,570 --> 00:33:42,290
It's said that once people are married, their feelings will be deep.

674
00:33:42,290 --> 00:33:44,970
I was so lucky to meet you.

675
00:33:45,330 --> 00:33:48,360
Riding the same boat needs ten years of cultivation.

676
00:33:48,710 --> 00:33:52,570
Sharing a bed and dreaming together need the fate of three lifetimes.

677
00:33:52,820 --> 00:33:55,590
I wanted to hold your hands under flowers,

678
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:57,150
cook with you,

679
00:33:57,690 --> 00:33:59,410
be a loving couple with you,

680
00:33:59,780 --> 00:34:01,500
and make others envy us.

681
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:04,470
But I was born into a family of coroners.

682
00:34:04,870 --> 00:34:06,580
I'm always looked down upon.

683
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:08,389
I'm not outgoing either.

684
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,340
It's hard for me to make you happy.

685
00:34:10,830 --> 00:34:12,429
I have skills,

686
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:14,409
but I make clay figurines to make a living,

687
00:34:14,409 --> 00:34:15,969
stop thieves from the tomb,

688
00:34:16,230 --> 00:34:17,909
and am not valued by the world.

689
00:34:18,870 --> 00:34:21,730
Seven years have passed, and discord has appeared.

690
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:25,000
The resentment is hard to resolve and has become deep.

691
00:34:25,310 --> 00:34:27,239
I wanted to change my temperament,

692
00:34:27,429 --> 00:34:29,190
but it's hard.

693
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:31,409
I wanted to left my job as a coroner,

694
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:33,440
but I fell for it over time.

695
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:36,870
While I look old, you look beautiful.

696
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:39,550
I can't delay you

697
00:34:39,949 --> 00:34:41,330
for this reason.

698
00:34:42,139 --> 00:34:45,219
Today, I let you go, which makes both of us happy.

699
00:34:45,830 --> 00:34:48,250
May you find a good husband.

700
00:34:48,750 --> 00:34:51,270
Raise children with a smile on your face.

701
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:55,190
The family members will be happy, and I won't have regrets.

702
00:34:56,440 --> 00:35:00,110
In order to leave a proof, I, Du Guyang, who's from Shiyang County of Yongzhou,

703
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:01,790
wrote this with respect.

704
00:35:09,750 --> 00:35:11,310
Dugu Yang.

705
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:14,600
This isn't a letter of divorce.

706
00:35:15,110 --> 00:35:17,910
Clearly, the whole letter is full of wistfulness.

707
00:35:18,990 --> 00:35:19,910
It seems

708
00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,840
that I, your wife,

709
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:24,630
am not that bad.

710
00:35:28,310 --> 00:35:29,970
My Dugu was so good at writing.

711
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:32,090
If he hadn't born into a family of coroners,

712
00:35:32,090 --> 00:35:35,870
he would have passed the imperial examination and become an imperial officer.

713
00:35:35,870 --> 00:35:36,930
Forget about that.

714
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:38,730
Being an imperial officer

715
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:40,410
is a dream of all scholars,

716
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:42,170
but there has to be someone

717
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:44,110
being a coroner.

718
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,910
Mr. Su. Physician Fei.

719
00:35:47,910 --> 00:35:48,430
Ladies.

720
00:35:48,430 --> 00:35:49,630
You came just in time.

721
00:35:49,750 --> 00:35:51,150
We have a big event today.

722
00:35:52,350 --> 00:35:53,870
Please witness it.

723
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:57,950
I, Cao Hui, the female coroner of Tang,

724
00:35:58,230 --> 00:36:00,950
will teach skills on behalf of my son Dugu Yang.

725
00:36:07,380 --> 00:36:08,900
Who is kneeling?

726
00:36:09,390 --> 00:36:10,590
The wife of Dugu Yang,

727
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:11,750
Chuntiao.

728
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:14,920
Do you volunteer to be a coroner?

729
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,270
Yes.

730
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:18,400
Once a coroner,

731
00:36:18,870 --> 00:36:20,230
always a coroner.

732
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:23,640
Chuntiao, will you regret it?

733
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,110
No, I won't.

734
00:36:28,390 --> 00:36:29,840
I should host it.

735
00:36:31,270 --> 00:36:33,470
Chuntiao, bow to your teacher.

736
00:36:35,350 --> 00:36:36,220
Bow.

737
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,850
The ceremony is completed.

738
00:36:55,330 --> 00:36:59,390
Congratulations! The coroner family has a successor.

739
00:37:01,430 --> 00:37:07,690
-Congratulations! The coroner family has a successor.
-Congratulations! The coroner family has a successor.

740
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:32,160
Aren't you cold?

741
00:37:35,830 --> 00:37:37,030
I'm a bit cold.

742
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:39,900
But it's good to be cold.

743
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:42,190
Cold makes people sober

744
00:37:42,650 --> 00:37:45,040
and makes me stop indulging

745
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:47,500
in the illusion of nightmares.

746
00:37:48,230 --> 00:37:50,090
You actually dreamed of the case?

747
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:52,030
Are you shrewd

748
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:54,350
or deliberate?

749
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:56,670
What you said

750
00:37:56,690 --> 00:37:58,680
are not good words.

751
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:01,870
Scold me if you want.

752
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,620
I just recovered.

753
00:38:04,470 --> 00:38:06,110
I have nowhere to hide.

754
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:08,030
A notice has been issued in Shiyang.

755
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:09,660
The Su Wuming from Chang'an

756
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:10,960
has already died.

757
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:12,390
You're safe now.

758
00:38:12,390 --> 00:38:13,990
But you haven't.

759
00:38:15,260 --> 00:38:16,190
What do you mean?

760
00:38:16,270 --> 00:38:18,360
The first poison dart

761
00:38:18,390 --> 00:38:20,710
shot by the assassin that day

762
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,910
didn't seem

763
00:38:23,270 --> 00:38:24,870
to be aimed at Dugu Xiashu.

764
00:38:26,150 --> 00:38:26,990
Dugu Xiashu?

765
00:38:27,710 --> 00:38:28,720
It's me.

766
00:38:28,750 --> 00:38:29,950
I'm a magistrate in Shiyang.

767
00:38:29,950 --> 00:38:31,410
-Welcome...
-Step aside!

768
00:38:35,070 --> 00:38:36,270
When I was in the dark,

769
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:37,990
the assassins had already taken action.

770
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:39,250
Don't get me involved.

771
00:38:39,470 --> 00:38:41,320
But you already said

772
00:38:42,270 --> 00:38:44,530
that there were two groups of assassins.

773
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:49,670
Su Wuming.

774
00:38:49,950 --> 00:38:51,520
Are you really not going to explain to me

775
00:38:51,520 --> 00:38:52,390
what happened

776
00:38:52,430 --> 00:38:53,230
in Chang'an?

777
00:38:54,770 --> 00:38:57,620
I did it for my own future.

778
00:38:57,950 --> 00:39:00,070
In order to get promoted and rich,

779
00:39:00,090 --> 00:39:01,310
I went to the palace

780
00:39:01,350 --> 00:39:02,880
and told the new emperor.

781
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:04,170
But in the end...

782
00:39:05,830 --> 00:39:07,110
This is such an embarrassing thing.

783
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,550
What is there to explain?

784
00:39:15,750 --> 00:39:17,840
If you don't want to explain it, forget it.

785
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,640
I'll see how long you can keep it.

786
00:39:20,190 --> 00:39:21,720
We're departing tomorrow.

787
00:39:23,590 --> 00:39:24,920
Would you like to go with us?

788
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:27,750
You've been in Shiyang for more than ten days.

789
00:39:27,870 --> 00:39:29,890
Aren't you waiting for me to recover?

790
00:39:29,890 --> 00:39:30,670
If I...

791
00:39:30,690 --> 00:39:31,620
I'm staying here

792
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:32,830
not for you,

793
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,950
but to help Dugu Xiashu

794
00:39:35,350 --> 00:39:37,630
bring peace back to Shiyang.

795
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:43,080
Are you going with us or not?

796
00:39:44,390 --> 00:39:45,520
I'm not

797
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:47,300
an ungrateful person.

798
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,500
But I have to have an identity

799
00:39:48,500 --> 00:39:49,690
if I go west with you.

800
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:52,190
How about being my personal secretary?

801
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:53,140
What's my monthly salary?

802
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:54,830
I'll give you one tenth of mine.

803
00:39:54,830 --> 00:39:56,220
One tenth?

804
00:39:56,430 --> 00:39:57,070
So little?

805
00:39:57,350 --> 00:39:58,630
When you went south with me before,

806
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,190
I...

807
00:39:59,270 --> 00:40:00,550
Did you ever pay me salary?

808
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,500
Didn't I?

809
00:40:05,130 --> 00:40:06,000
Just one tenth.

810
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:07,660
We're departing tomorrow morning.

811
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:08,460
If you think it's little,

812
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:09,390
don't follow us.

813
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:11,340
Anyway, Yingtao told Xijun

814
00:40:11,790 --> 00:40:13,270
that she'll go with us

815
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:14,970
to see the magnificent mountains and rivers

816
00:40:14,970 --> 00:40:16,290
of Tang.

817
00:40:17,590 --> 00:40:18,270
Lu Lingfeng.

818
00:40:18,270 --> 00:40:19,000
Lu Lingfeng!

819
00:40:19,390 --> 00:40:21,390
Let's talk about the salary.

820
00:40:21,750 --> 00:40:24,590
Raise it a bit.

821
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:34,910
Dugu.

822
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:36,900
From now on,

823
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:39,020
everything will depend on you.

824
00:40:39,390 --> 00:40:40,270
Remember,

825
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,790
the point of being an official

826
00:40:43,190 --> 00:40:45,670
is to do more practical things for people.

827
00:40:46,310 --> 00:40:47,790
In doing so,

828
00:40:47,990 --> 00:40:49,910
you can sleep well, eat well,

829
00:40:50,430 --> 00:40:51,990
and feel at ease.

830
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:56,890
I was educated.

831
00:40:57,500 --> 00:40:58,110
By the way,

832
00:40:58,790 --> 00:40:59,510
is

833
00:40:59,990 --> 00:41:02,720
the Dugu Xin Jet Tumbled Stone Multifaceted Seal

834
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:04,390
a legend

835
00:41:04,410 --> 00:41:05,930
or a real thing?

836
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,310
You have to

837
00:41:07,420 --> 00:41:08,710
solve this mystery.

838
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:09,790
Okay.

839
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:11,710
I'll keep that in mind

840
00:41:11,990 --> 00:41:13,320
until I find the answer.

841
00:41:13,750 --> 00:41:14,630
Please wait.

842
00:41:17,290 --> 00:41:18,720
Take the naan I made

843
00:41:18,990 --> 00:41:19,920
to eat on the way.

844
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:21,110
Mr. Ma, thank you.

845
00:41:21,350 --> 00:41:22,010
General Lu.

846
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,200
You cleared my name.

847
00:41:27,310 --> 00:41:28,310
You're my savior.

848
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,910
Please accept my bow.

849
00:41:34,740 --> 00:41:36,180
Although there is no chicken,

850
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:37,710
I have to thank you.

851
00:41:39,750 --> 00:41:40,320
Alright.

852
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:43,750
It's time to say goodbye.

853
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:45,110
Guys.

854
00:41:45,510 --> 00:41:46,270
Stay.

855
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,190
Goodbye.

856
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:53,790
Mr. Su.

857
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:56,090
General Lu.

858
00:41:57,430 --> 00:41:58,290
Physician Fei.

859
00:41:59,830 --> 00:42:00,540
Miss Xijun.

860
00:42:01,910 --> 00:42:02,910
Heroine Yingtao.

861
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:05,840
If you have friends who know your heart,

862
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,470
Distance cannot keep you apart.

