00:42:07,470 --> 00:42:09,330
At crossroads where we bid adieu,

864
00:42:09,350 --> 00:42:10,940
Do not shed tears as women do!

865
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:12,540
With the lines of Wang Zi'an,

866
00:42:15,870 --> 00:42:17,000
I'm sending you off.

867
00:42:30,540 --> 00:42:32,750
I found the right person.

868
00:42:33,430 --> 00:42:34,890
Brother, what do you mean?

869
00:42:40,230 --> 00:42:42,040
If you think this wood carving

870
00:42:42,070 --> 00:42:43,030
is good,

871
00:42:43,910 --> 00:42:45,080
please cherish it

872
00:42:45,830 --> 00:42:46,990
and never give it up.

873
00:42:47,870 --> 00:42:48,670
It'd be better

874
00:42:49,910 --> 00:42:51,030
to pass it down.

875
00:42:52,470 --> 00:42:53,150
Brother!

876
00:42:57,810 --> 00:42:59,210
Why did Brother come to me

877
00:43:00,490 --> 00:43:01,500
in my dream?

878
00:44:02,030 --> 00:44:02,550
This...

879
00:44:07,620 --> 00:44:09,620
This is Brother's family heirloom.

880
00:44:09,710 --> 00:44:11,440
Please take it back and keep it.

881
00:44:12,100 --> 00:44:13,630
There really is such a seal.

882
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:14,870
Let me see.

883
00:44:24,450 --> 00:44:25,460
What a treasure.

884
00:44:29,550 --> 00:44:30,480
What do you mean?

885
00:44:30,490 --> 00:44:32,300
He entrusted this seal to you.

886
00:44:32,790 --> 00:44:33,710
It's yours.

887
00:44:34,790 --> 00:44:35,360
No.

888
00:44:35,800 --> 00:44:37,270
You must keep it for him.

889
00:44:38,500 --> 00:44:40,030
This isn't just a treasure.

890
00:44:40,870 --> 00:44:42,400
This is the life of Dugu Yang

891
00:44:42,780 --> 00:44:44,270
and the Dugu family.

892
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:46,540
Physician Fei has treated Mother for days.

893
00:44:46,540 --> 00:44:47,190
My mother

894
00:44:47,220 --> 00:44:48,480
has almost recovered.

895
00:44:48,710 --> 00:44:51,190
She told me that many years ago,

896
00:44:51,390 --> 00:44:52,450
Dugu Yang's father

897
00:44:52,670 --> 00:44:54,310
would rather marry into a coroner family

898
00:44:54,310 --> 00:44:55,470
than sell this seal.

899
00:44:55,910 --> 00:44:57,520
He only had one condition.

900
00:44:57,820 --> 00:45:00,750
If he had descendants, their surname should be Dugu.

901
00:45:01,510 --> 00:45:03,470
He entrusted this seal to you.

902
00:45:03,490 --> 00:45:05,950
It must be because your surname is also Dugu.

903
00:45:06,870 --> 00:45:08,270
Please cherish this seal

904
00:45:08,650 --> 00:45:09,960
and pass it down

905
00:45:09,990 --> 00:45:11,790
from generation to generation.

906
00:45:12,790 --> 00:45:13,590
Please.

907
00:45:21,110 --> 00:45:22,370
I'll keep that in mind.

908
00:45:23,670 --> 00:45:24,200
This seal

909
00:45:24,760 --> 00:45:26,490
is the treasure of our country.

910
00:45:26,910 --> 00:45:27,930
Thousands of years later,

911
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:29,510
it'll surely shine brightly

912
00:45:29,510 --> 00:45:30,710
and comfort Brother.

913
00:45:37,350 --> 00:45:37,960
By the way,

914
00:45:40,050 --> 00:45:41,310
how interesting it is.

915
00:45:44,060 --> 00:45:46,390
Yesterday, Dugu Yang came to me in my dream

916
00:45:46,670 --> 00:45:49,350
and asked me to invite you to the house for some soup noodles.

917
00:45:49,350 --> 00:45:50,400
If you want to eat,

918
00:45:51,470 --> 00:45:52,270
come anytime.

919
00:45:57,500 --> 00:45:58,390
Thank you.
